---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Section from "../components/Section.astro";
import Container from "../components/Container.astro";
import Columns from "../components/Columns.astro";
import ButtonGroup from "../components/ButtonGroup.astro";
import Button from "../components/Button.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon";
import LogoCarousel from "../components/LogoCarousel.astro";
import Article from "../components/Article.astro";
import CardWrapper from "../components/CardWrapper.astro";
import TestimonialWrapper from "../components/TestimonialWrapper.astro";
import CTA from "../components/CTA.astro";
---

<Layout>
  <Section>
    <Container>
      <Columns>
        <div slot="first">
          <p class="eyebrow">FREE Masterclass for engineers and tech workers</p>
          <h1 class="hero--heading">
            The <span class="span">4 Keys</span> to Intentional Engineering Career
            Transitions
          </h1>
          <ButtonGroup>
            <Button
              href="https://morethan-engineering.com/eca-masterclass/"
              isBlank="true"
              label="Watch now"
            >
              <Icon pack="heroicons-solid" name="play" slot="icon--left" />
            </Button>
            <Button isOutlined="true" href="#career" label="Learn more">
              <Icon pack="heroicons-solid" name="arrow-right" slot="icon--right"
              />
            </Button>
          </ButtonGroup>
        </div>
        <div slot="second"></div>
      </Columns>
    </Container>
    <div class="section--wrapper">
      <img src="/assets/jeff-perry-cutout.webp" alt="" class="hero--cutout" />
      <img src="/assets/background-icons.svg" alt="" class="hero--background" />
    </div>
  </Section>
  <LogoCarousel />
  <Section>
    <div id="career" class="career--anchor"></div>
    <Container>
      <Article>
        <h2>Your Career Engineered</h2>
        <p>
          Each of us has unlimited potential. Too often we place limits on
          ourselves, which can then limit those around us.
        </p>
        <p>
          To unlock your potential, you can look to the fundamental laws of the
          universe that can be applied to you.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong
            >You can be more than an engineer, scientist, or whatever your
            chosen profession is.
          </strong>
        </p>
        <p>
          You can be a human that is full of life, bringing opportunities,
          innovations, and lasting impact to those around you. Each day should
          be seen as an opportunity to do great things and touch the lives of
          others. Don't let a day pass you by wihtout doing something you are
          proud of, learning something new, or strengthening a relationship.
        </p>
        <p>Life can be scary, uncertain, and stressful.</p>
        <p>
          But life can also be fun, beautiful, and full of joy! Much of what we
          experience in life is due to our choices, and I hope to inspire you to
          make choices that will create a life you are proud of.
        </p>
        <p>
          Each of us needs help and assistance on the road of life. I want to do
          my part to help you grow as an individual, leader, husband, wife,
          sibling, parent, friend, or whatever other roles you fill in life.
          Together we'll create goals and systems to achieve them, increase
          personal growth, and create career fulfillment.
        </p>
        <p>
          Some of the things you are asked to do might seem crazy or out of your
          comfort zone. Some ideas might seem like common sense. You'll only get
          results if you take action.
        </p>
        <p>
          You are more than an engineerâ€”let's work together to design an amazing
          career and life for you!
        </p>
      </Article>
    </Container>
  </Section>
  <Section>
    <Container>
      <CardWrapper />
    </Container>
  </Section>
  <Section>
    <Container>
      <Columns>
        <div slot="first" class="about--left">
          <h2>
            <span class="span">About</span> Jeff Perry
          </h2>
          <div class="about--subheading">
            <p>
              Hi, I'm Jeff Perry, a leadership and career coach for engineers.
            </p>
            <p>
              I LOVE seeing my clients upgrade their mindsets, lives, and
              careers as we take a holistic approach to personal development.
            </p>
            <p>
              You should be <strong>transforming</strong> into a better person in
              all facets of life.
            </p>
            <p>Sound interesting? Click the link below to learn more.</p>
          </div>
          <Button isOutlined="true" href="/about" label="Learn more">
            <Icon pack="heroicons-solid" name="arrow-right" slot="icon--right"
            />
          </Button>
        </div>
        <div slot="second">
          <img src="/assets/jeff-perry-about.webp" alt="" class="about--img" />
        </div>
        <Columns />
      </Columns>
    </Container>
  </Section>
  <Section>
    <Container>
      <TestimonialWrapper />
    </Container>
  </Section>
  <CTA />

  <style lang="scss">
    @import "../styles/variables.scss";
    :global(.eyebrow) {
      margin-bottom: map-get($spacing, "600");
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    [astro-icon] {
      display: inline-block;
      width: 1.25rem;
      height: 1.25rem;
    }

    .section--wrapper {
      position: absolute;
      z-index: 50;
      top: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: map-get($breakpoints, "xxl");
      height: 100%;
      margin-inline: auto;
    }

    .hero--cutout {
      display: none;
      position: absolute;
      z-index: 100;
      right: map-get($spacing-pairs, "from-400-to-900");
      bottom: 0;
      width: auto;
      height: 35rem;

      @media screen and (min-width: map-get($breakpoints, "lg")) {
        display: block;
      }
    }

    .hero--background {
      display: none;
      position: absolute;
      z-index: 50;
      top: 0;
      right: 0;
      bottom: 0;
      width: auto;
      height: 100%;
      opacity: 0.75;

      @media screen and (min-width: map-get($breakpoints, "lg")) {
        display: block;
      }
    }

    .hero--heading {
      line-height: 1.125;
      margin-bottom: map-get($spacing, "600");
    }

    :global(.span) {
      padding: 0.25rem 1rem;
      background-color: map-get($primary, "500");
      color: white;
    }

    .career--anchor {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      right: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      visibility: hidden;
    }

    .about--left {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: flex-start;
      height: 100%;
    }

    .about--img {
      box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba($black, 0.1);
    }

    h2 {
      margin-bottom: map-get($spacing, "400");
    }
    .about--subheading {
      margin-bottom: map-get($spacing, "600");
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
